{"tid":1027370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公院爆煲，醫護人員都爆煲，真係好慘","createTime":"2019-02-18T18:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T22:37:19.000Z","uid":33330,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e860a9b64655b4469dfddb957410f1cdf98d267e","tid":1027370,"uid":33330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T18:59:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinefansclub/videos/264256774473576?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnextmagazinefansclub%2Fvideos%2F264256774473576%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=XUHW2qJizO2pFN7N4VPpEoPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=47857d46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinefansclub/videos/264256774473576?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n讀咁多書，入到神科<br />\n應該諗到有美好既將來<br />\n終於畢業<br />\n出到黎做醫生<br />\n得到既竟然係非人既生活<br />\n到底呢個香港仲有冇得救<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家如果去公院睇病<br />\n尊重醫護人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有醫護人員睇到呢度<br />\n我真心真意地多謝你地既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d163c2070e90c4a3d6518ed189dd2f2a38aa6b","tid":1027370,"uid":138233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7de95dafe0f60d21dbf70d54afe1ce19b6df8b","tid":1027370,"uid":138233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a556a4be489acff60e42d31b4df44e0a5409e5aa","tid":1027370,"uid":138233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T19:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5484ec7b25538b7cff2f7b0054b04e1e609e70ae","tid":1027370,"uid":59528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:02:22.000Z","msg":"替佢地覺得辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f5545eec2bce12b60a89e1385e4af17e0af315","tid":1027370,"uid":101110,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:20:38.000Z","msg":"香港醫生真係世界級㗎啦<br />\n沙士嗰陣係邊個留落嚟救人<br />\n回歸後邊條粉皮減醫護人手<br />\n<br />\n救你條命仲要受你氣<br />\n想做好啲關心多啲病人又無時間無精神，咁撚多人點做得完<br />\n竟然仲有某部分連登仔自命清高為民請命日日屌醫生護士<br />\n<br />\n香港回歸後都係得一個問題，人太多<br />\n而且仲要係劣質人種太多<br />\n<br />\n依一代有能力有知識嘅唔洗諗賺夠一定又移民，到時用緊醫療服務嘅已經係支那人，所以醫生護士係支那人，高層都會係支那人。五十年不變，一國兩制完埋，大家無錢嘅唔會醫你，醫療質素唔會再有保證。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話我悲觀，港獨唔係100%唔得，但事實上依家係癌症擴散到所有器官。你諗到嘅，諗唔到嘅地方，高中低層都俾支那入侵晒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫療都只不過係反映香港現況與未來，多謝晒為病人辛勞嘅前線醫護人員。<br />\n<br />\n依個世界係無報應㗎你放心，香港政府官員、醫管局高層依然都係會活很好過我哋啲普通市民。因為佢哋就係有錢有權又生喺最好嘅時代，過多廿年中帶承諾嘅五十年不變之前班人都死咗，佢哋後代都移民做美國人英國人。<br />\n<br />\n香港人？早已經唔存在啦。"},{"pid":"2718b4052bbd29a018aef92a1a30722e4a0a0cc7","tid":1027370,"uid":75195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:22:37.000Z","msg":"共匪真係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9c285d4055190edea4dcfc3d14dd5d287adb72","tid":1027370,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:23:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c92d400aefef65e603b2a89488dfcd6bf922a9e6","tid":1027370,"uid":141901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:24:55.000Z","msg":"香港人 我地團結踢走150個配額<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要成功 先要有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">信念</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">團結</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">爭氣</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee22f38ecd5d95c51b90f51167b8ef583d5d497d","tid":1027370,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:45:31.000Z","msg":"請問邊行唔慘?<br />\n入行之前唔知?<br />\n咁揾萬零兩萬, 要識飛, 又要ot 到8,9 點果班點算?"},{"pid":"33dc5995535a2292845b93f985ae70b06c328d7e","tid":1027370,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee22f38ecd5d95c51b90f51167b8ef583d5d497d","tid":1027370,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:45:31.000Z","msg":"請問邊行唔慘?<br />\n入行之前唔知?<br />\n咁揾萬零兩萬, 要識飛, 又要ot 到8,9 點果班點算?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T20:47:09.000Z","msg":"之前已經仆街 <br />\n現在大陸玩埋依D野 <br />\n真係搵狗都唔做"},{"pid":"9729abb337e5c390dd2c078b5a178bf797b69a25","ti